      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GLIMMERING (4) flew the lids and led throughout to score a most impressive win by 7 lengths at this track over 460m (26.00). Comes through a solid form race last start. Expected to be right there at the finish again. PAY THE REG (7) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (26.19) at this track behind Smooth Prince in a Bottom Up - Grade 5. Took the lead and boxed on but run over. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Must be included in calculations. KING OF PAIN (3) finds it hard to win. Finished second (24.94) at Sale latest and might be close to finding winning form again. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from four starts. Can measure up. CHEER DOWN (2) is not to be discarded.",
